<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ الكِتَابَةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَهِيَ:</span> بَيْعُ عَبْدِهِ نَفْسَهُ، بِمَالٍ مُؤَجَّلٍ فِي ذِمَّتِهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَتُسَنُّ:</span> مَعَ أَمَانَةِ العَبْدِ وَكَسْبِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَتُكْرَهُ:</span> مَعَ عَدَمِهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَيَجُوزُ بَيْعُ المُكَاتَبِ، وَمُشْتَرِيهِ يَقُومُ مَقَامَ مُكَاتِبِهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">فَإِنْ أَدَّى:</span> عَتَقَ، وَوَلَاؤُهُ لَهُ،<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ عَجَزَ:</span> عَادَ قِنًّا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>* * *<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>